title: [Malwith Inn, Balcony]
description: The city seems to fan out from the balcony.  Elaborately turned posts support the short railing around the balcony.  A potted fern hangs from an iron hook attached to the inn wall.

The city seems to fan out from the balcony.  Elaborately turned posts support the short railing around the balcony.  A potted fern hangs from an iron hook attached to the inn wall.  Moonlight bathes the balcony in a pale glow.
